	 whose seemingly effortless momentum carries the joy of its creation witho
	ut ignoring the darkness pervading our consciousness. Led by guitarist/voc
	alist Ripley Johnson\\\, the music of Rose City Band is rooted in his love
	 of private press records of the mid to late 70s. The band\\\, in addition
	 to Johnson\\\, features pedal steel guitarist Barry Walker\\\, keyboardis
